ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"首先<span style=\"color: red;\">我地自己嘅訴求都仲未得到答覆</span>，<br />\n依家就個個都話要幫武漢乜 武漢物，<br />\n想點？想分資源去做鄰國野？<br />\n下邊個post我睇到嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">想模糊大家嘅焦點</span>，<br />\n話乜撚野拎光環，要比全世界知香港唔同中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前仲拎唔夠咩？<br />\n同埋大家唔好唔記得我地嘅目標係乜野，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係度呼籲大家 抵制聲援武漢，見一個屌一個</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「各有各做」如果唔聲援武漢 你憑咩叫外國幫你香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"你既意思繫懷疑<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢示威者系鬼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a16a82db60e58eacce1aeef84da487d085601f","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6904f309ed7ed22cb3d19fb6e8c7e8ee0f76aebd","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a759ab19d3de9e387339e182ed632eac2e9a27f","tid":1287062,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"唔好比人分散焦點啊!<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cfa242cdf38c1dfb6a4196234c370290c6d92f","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6337ef72786a32da0952a22c73ab2fb713200e8","tid":1287062,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"鄰国武漢關我地撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da3b65cf27621457dc507c3b84b6b6e7ad88d68","tid":1287062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"樓主係變相割蓆？"},{"pid":"1b63f55a8b415892b417241f5987002a04edb451","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da3b65cf27621457dc507c3b84b6b6e7ad88d68","tid":1287062,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"樓主係變相割蓆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"追一追post先 ok?"},{"pid":"3756e7328f0edaae7d59596d285a31ee781148c5","tid":1287062,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"敵人個敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcbbb73cffc02a6cf513561301df1d302b6b40c","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b728bd519e742c2326cacf11a36664f31e0a1eda","tid":1287062,"uid":268720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:28:04.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">講下自己既愚見\n\n我認同 7.7 要集中講同強調 5 大訴求\n凝聚力量，唔可以分心，同比其他野搞散個氣勢\n\n我都理解點解有人會覺得要「講一吓」武漢單野\n就好似有巴打分析點解台灣會幫香港出聲，甚至連冇直接關係既日本或其他國家都出聲\n\n無他，因為香港係世界棋局上面一隻有能力牽制中共既棋，簡單講就係有利用價值\n其他野我唔講，只講感染力，香港就做到令中共憂慮既感染力\n所以提一提武漢，唔係壞事，無須多，多就消耗自己既資源同衝散我地本身既訴求，可能只須一句，例如「強烈譴責武漢政府血腥鎮壓市民」就足夠\n利用香港本身既感染力，將信息透過自由行，帶入內地慢慢發酵\n武漢單野可以話係一個藥引，提升香港反送中運動既散播力，因為始終對自由行來講，自己國內既事會比香港既事更吸引</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a8409a5119705cd87702cae8aafec2d6b4017df6","tid":1287062,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人真係痴鳩線，抱薪救火</span></blockquote>台灣人真係痴鳩線，抱薪救火<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">[精彩好文]PTT有人解釋點解台灣人<span style=\"color: red;\">一定</span>要撐香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1232173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1232173</a></span></blockquote><br />\n你個名出賣咗你啦</blockquote>可唔可以理性討論？<br />\n<br />\n講個 point 嚟反駁？</blockquote><br />\n台灣人同香港人情況相近，面臨接管邊緣，唇亡齒寒<br />\n<br />\n香港人同大陸人河水不犯，目標又唔同，佢地反共先出聲啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪誇大到&ldquo;一定&ldquo;要幫，到台灣大選前夕，香港都一定唔會勉強 / 能夠體諒台灣人的處境"},{"pid":"8819075b5d7f774b47311937317dff58f34d3a6f","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c8c74e55c7c323f99612671938febf71a7c510f","tid":1287062,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f3b57206cb88fb8ba74a8b921b0dd51ec1bbd3","tid":1287062,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1518e774491b883423fb2c5bc3c84c2c8440063","tid":1287062,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d4e6cb147b3d0f1c7f497713b4c6d55f65d75c","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a5d7c304e481dc83df833425c1c35806b06acb2","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cef0362f0246a0b3d36b050ea758735d1cb175a","tid":1287062,"uid":92299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔逐一回覆反對我嘅人<br />\n我一次過係度講，<br />\n開呢個post嘅目的只有一個<br />\n就係叫大家專注反係我地自己嘅訴求度，<br />\n當下最主要係集中搞好自己屋企<br />\n乜撚野武漢、64，等一切完左<br />\n我話之你幫佢地做文宣定苦行，我理撚得你點做<br />\n唔好再講乜撚野話借武漢令到鄰國醒覺嘅廢話，<br />\n因為做慣奴隸係永遠唔會知乜野叫民主</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"de81feca943b590f1469dea818fd2a9202611fd6